Yuji Itadori is a boy with tremendous physical strength, though he lives a completely ordinary high school life. One day, to save a classmate who has been attacked by curses, he eats the finger of Ryomen Sukuna, taking the curse into his own soul. From then on, he shares one body with Ryomen Sukuna. Guided by the most powerful of sorcerers, Satoru Gojo, Itadori is admitted to Tokyo Jujutsu High School, an organization that fights the curses... and thus begins the heroic tale of a boy who became a curse to exorcise a curse, a life from which he could never turn back.

I’m not fuckin with your guest list,

Bolunga mai jhoot nahi, taanay kiun bandook nai, 
finger on the trigger, I’m confused, what’s the truth bae,
I know when your mood swings
Agar mai nai tera saqi, gallay se utrega ghunt nahi,
Nasha tera kaafi, koshish girnay na den boond koi,
Khone ko nai baaqi kuch ye dunya mujhse rooth gayi, loot gayiii
tu hai taara magar toot nahi, 
Pathar tera dil, kyun samandar mai tu doob gayi,
Shehr e dil mai tere tikta nahi hoon,
Mai likhta raha gaanay, mai rukta nahi hoon, 
Wo mera bahaana, mai unka nahi hoon,
Mai tere sirhaanay, kyun dikhta nahi hoon,
Bhatka musaafir, tu hi mera ghar, 
Tu hi meri manzil, tu hi mera darr, 
Mai darbadar jo tu na hoti agar,
Dil mai jo baaten, sab kehden, magar...

Kya ye teri saza 
Ya ye meri hai dua 
Ya ye meri hai dua

Faraib main bhi kaisy farhat Zamana sangdil hai kyun 
Ab tu hai recklesss talking to ur exes
Dont fucking test me i barely pass it I smoke and pass shit 
Saari raat nashey saari baat ye kay Loyalty’s everything bae
Teray bin kitnay din katey 
Teray bin zinda reh gaye Teray bin jee to nai sakay
Dil jalay aur sar phiray 
I smoke trees and home rochies kill karain 
Ham chill to hain 
Bolo kitna chill karain ham miltay hain 
Mil kay bhi miltay nai ye silsilay 
Shuru huwey thay kya dil say nai main sensitive 
Par abhi senses main nai When i pen this down to pehlay sansani 
Kay meray dil ki raahein saari band pareen 
Tunay haal bhula diya kal kay liye 
Haath uthay hain to rab kay liye 
Koi ni mera main sab kay liye 
Likhay ye geet apney ghar kay liye 
Likhnay day rab umar bhar kay liye 
Wo jaaney muje meri shafqat kay liye 
Na jaaney muje meray shar kay liye 
Ye kala bani meri manzil
Main to likha karta tha safar kay liye 
Ye ghar mera ye sab mera nahi
Kyun likhun is deewaro dar kay liye (yeah)

snippet.title: Baahubali: The Epic - Official Trailer (2025)
snippet.description:
Before RRR took the world by storm, master filmmaker S.S. Rajamouli redefined Indian Cinema with his two-part BAAHUBALI saga. Now, the epic tale of royalty, revenge, kings, and wars has been personally re-edited by the master himself from two films into a single unforgettable cinematic experience, with fully remastered picture and sound (and a few new surprises), so audiences can reunite to experience the euphoria the way it was intended: on the big screen, together. 

When a lost prince is rescued and raised in exile, he grows up unaware of his past. Years later, he returns to uncover the truth about his father’s murder and his mother’s imprisonment, and must rise to reclaim his place as the rightful king.

Baahubali: The Epic will be released in theaters across the U.S. October 31st.

#IGN #Movies

snippet.title: Do You Wanna Partner - Official Trailer | Tamannaah Bhatia, Diana Penty | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Do You Wanna Partner Official Trailer
Starring Tamannaah Bhatia, Diana Penty, Jaaved Jaaferi, Nakuul Mehta, Neeraj Kabi, Shweta Tiwari, Sufi Motiwala, Rannjivay Singha, Lokesh Mittal, Indranil Sengupta, Ayesha Raza
Directed by Archit Kumar and Collin D'Cunha
Written by Nandini Gupta, Aarsh Vora and Mithun Gangopadhyay
Created by Mithun Gangopadhyay and Nishant Nayak
A Dharmatic Entertainment Production

Official Release Date September 12, 2025 on Prime Video India.

About:
Best friends Shikha and Anahita turn entrepreneurs with an exciting craft beer brand, Jugaaro, to stand out in the crowded NCR beer market. However, they face gender discrimination every step of the way. To fight for an equal place in this male dominated sector, they decide to invent a fictitious male partner to help smooth their way. Invariably, things don’t go exactly as planned. What follows are their collective adventures & misadventures in trying to build a successful start-up amidst the current boom, as the bunch of misfits band together and become a family.

Follow us on:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/primevideoin/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PrimeVideoIN/
X: https://x.com/PrimeVideoIN

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO

snippet.title: Dolphins Up Close with Bertie Gregory | Official Trailer | National Geographic
snippet.description:
Bertie Gregory heads to the Azores, a remote island chain in the Atlantic Ocean. Surrounded by Europe’s largest marine protected area, these waters are a vital stop for migrating predators, drawn here by rich feeding grounds. It’s the perfect time for Bertie to capture a rare natural spectacle—when elusive predators unite to hunt dense shoals of fish called bait balls. But with unpredictable storms, filming won’t be easy. During his journey, Bertie also explores the region’s dark history of marine exploitation. By meeting an ex-whaler turned whale spotter, he discovers how the end of whaling transformed the Azores into a sanctuary, allowing marine life to return and delicate food chains to thrive.

YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2", the sixth film in the YRF Spy Universe, starring Hrithik Roshan, NTR and Kiara Advani, directed by Ayan Mukerji, released on 14 August 2025. snippet.title: Alice In Borderland Season 3 | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
The survival action series "Alice in Borderland" became the most watched Japanese Netflix title by worldwide audiences.

Now, the "games" that took the world by storm begin once again.

In the previous season, Arisu (#KentoYamazaki) and Usagi (#TaoTsuchiya) cleared all of the games and returned to the real world. They have since gotten married and established a happy life together. Their memories of the borderland were erased, but they see glimpses of it in dreams and hallucinations. One day, Usagi, led by afterlife researcher Ryuji (#KentoKaku), suddenly vanishes. At the same time as Usagi's disappearance, Banda (#HayatoIsomura) hands Arisu the final card: the Joker.

The uncharted journey led by the mysterious Joker card is about to unfold...

Season 3 of the Netflix Series "Alice in Borderland" is set for worldwide release on Thursday, September 25, 2025, only on Netflix.

#AliceinBorderlandS3, #AliceinBorderland3, #Netflix

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81682895

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Alice In Borderland Season 3 | Official Trailer | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

When a morbid professor pulls Usagi back to Borderland, Arisu goes after her. But can he survive a new round of deadly games and escape the Joker's plans?
